            . I am a pawnbroker, and live in Stanhope-street, Clare-market. On the 2d of February the prisoner pledged a coat, waistcoat, and a pair of trowsers, with me.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190217-54-person591">
                  THOMAS 
                  TAYLOR
               <interp inst="t18190217-54-person591" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
