                     <interp inst="t18190217-54-person592" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Turner, who is a pawnbroker, and lives in Bridge-street. On the 2d of February the prisoner pledged a suit of clothes with me.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 24.</p>
               <p>
